    <li class="fragment">CSS Layout</li>
    <li class="fragment">Flexbox</li>
    <li class="fragment">Using JavaScript to Manipulate Styles (which brings us to&#8230;)</li>
  </ul>

  <aside class="notes">
* know html? 
* know css?
* who's built a mobile ready site? what are some considerations when going from desktop to tablet or phone? think interaction design?
	* perhaps touch vs click/hover
	* resolution, obvs
	* performance / size
</aside>
</section>

